snippet.textDisplay:
this song is fun ,bubbly and what not. 😀 this song gives  positive and happy vibes 😊. the singers did a great job as usual.  good to see new faces and woah they enjoyed so much while singing . the guy who has the base voice ( he is paar channa de singer right ? ) he was also great 😍Ali sethi man !!! he can sing a song like aaqa and then he sings a ghazal ,gives  western  or pop touch  to songs like umraan langiyan and can also go  with  Desi beats. the orchestra as usually was fantastic because it's coke studio ;) . great guys _/\_   but then there were so many awesome songs last season so the expectation is very high from our side this time .but nonetheless keep making great songs 
-lot of love and respect from india
